    <content:encoded><![CDATA[《火星救援》剧本作者、《林中小屋》的导演 Drew Goddard 将为华纳兄弟编导一部新的《黑客帝国》电影。《黑客帝国》系列影片的联合编剧和导演 Lana Wachowski 将担任执行制片人，系列电影的主演 Keanu Reeves、Carrie Anne-Moss、Laurence Fishburne、Hugo Weaving 和 Jada Pinkett Smith 是否回归未知。华纳兄弟电影制作公司总裁 Jesse Ehrman 表示，Drew 带来了新的创意，我们相信它既能以全新的方式延续《黑客帝国》世界，又尊重了 Wachowsk 姐妹，并根据他本人对该系统及其角色的热爱提供了独特的视角。
<br>
https://deadline.com/2024/04/the-matrix-drew-goddard-1235874947/<br /><hr />
<p><a href="https://deadline.com/2024/04/the-matrix-drew-goddard-1235874947/" target="_blank">https://deadline.com/2024/04/the-matrix-drew-goddard-1235874947/</a></p>
<div>
<img src="https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Drew-Goddard-The-Matrix.jpg?w=681&amp;h=383&amp;crop=1" alt="Drew Goddard and The Matrix movie">
</div>
<figcaption>
<span>Drew Goddard, 'The Matrix'</span>
<span>Getty Images/Everett</span>
</figcaption>
<div>
<p>
<a href="https://deadline.com/tag/drew-goddard/" data-tag="drew-goddard">Drew Goddard</a>, the Oscar-nominated screenwriter of <em>The Martian</em> who also directed <em>The Cabin in the Woods</em>, has been set to write and direct a new <em>Matrix </em>movie at <a href="https://deadline.com/tag/warner-bros/" data-tag="warner-bros">Warner Bros</a>. The franchise’s original co-scribe and co-director Lana Wachowski is executive producing. </p>
<p>
It’s still early days in regards to whether core cast members Keanu Reeves, Carrie Anne-Moss, Laurence Fishburne, Hugo Weaving and Jada Pinkett Smith are coming back. </p>
<p>
Goddard will produce with partner Sarah Esberg (<em>Moonlight, If Beale Street Could Talk</em>)&nbsp;via their&nbsp;Goddard Textiles banner.
